Data Exploration: CalGEM Production

Descriptive statistics

  • The dataset includes observations from 122222 wells, 1999-2017
  • 17233732 observations include an observation for oil or gas production, and 10674563 of those had production > 0 barrels

Missingness

  • Of the 10674563 well-months with oil/gas production, in the dataset, 326029 (3.1%) are missing lat/long data
  • Volume of oil/gas with missing lat/long data
  • This isnt ideal, but I think were okay to move forward with these data! Particulary for 2001-2013 (see plots below)
